    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Astralith</strong> is a mutiplayer RPG where every character truly stands on their own. Collect dozens of spells and weapons, customize your character, and battle against other players all striving to reach the Astralith. Play a traveler in the woods, a merchant in the city, a mage in a tower, or even a king if you dare to reach for a throne.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Spellcraft:</strong> Collect spells as you level up to create unique combinations.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Personalization:</strong> Pick from a number of races to start with and dress them to appear just as you like.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Permadeath:</strong> Beware! Astralith takes death seriously, and if your character dies, they're dead for good.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can read more &amp; talk with other players in our discord: </p>",
